Data.Tips2: In general, Caster characters do well with items that have +Mana Points, +Mana Regeneration, +Spell Damage, and +Movement Speed. Caster characters can often benefit from Legendary items with activatable abilities.
Data.Name: game_character_displayname_AniviaEgg
Data.Passive1Desc: Annie's psychic powers allow her to generate mana quickly.

Unknown.70667387: In general, Caster characters should not buy items that have +Damage, +Attack Rate, or +Critical Rate.
Unknown.4243215484: As time passed, she became the cause of much trouble in Jugo. People became afraid of Annie because of the sudden fires that erupted when the little girl was in a bad mood. Several years later, she threw a temper tantrum over a dropped teddy bear, and completely incinerated her parents and her home. She has since drifted aimlessly from town to town, sometimes becoming angry over a trivial matter at which point great fire storms erupt leaving only a crying orphan girl in their wake. When the darkness inside of her felt the first call of Chaos, it discovered befitting and truly sinister use for the Dark Child.
